## 🏗️ SHOPIFY THEME — POORA SYSTEM SAMJHAO

### LESSON 1 — Theme Kya Hai?

Shopify theme ek **complete website package** hai.
Isko samjho jaise ek **ghar ka blueprint**:

```
Ghar ka blueprint = Theme
Kamre ki drawing = Template files
Har kamre ka saman = Sections
Saman ka design = Snippets
Ghar ka rang/style = CSS assets
Ghar ki bijli = JavaScript assets
Ghar ka address book = Config files
```

Jab koi tumhara store kholta hai:
1. Shopify URL dhundhta hai
2. Sahi template file dhundhti hai
3. Template mein jo sections hain woh load hoti hain
4. Sections mein jo snippets hain woh render hoti hain
5. CSS aur JS load hote hain
6. Merchant ki settings apply hoti hain
7. Page display hota hai

