### LESSON 9 — Ek File Banana Ka Complete Process

```
STEP 1: Plan karo
         Kya banana hai? Kya features chahiye?

STEP 2: File banao
         sections/my-section.liquid

STEP 3: Liquid HTML likho
         {% for block in section.blocks %}...{% endfor %}

STEP 4: CSS likho (scoped)
         #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} { ... }

STEP 5: JavaScript likho (IIFE)
         (function(){ ... })();

STEP 6: Schema likho
         {% schema %}{ ... }{% endschema %}

STEP 7: Template mein add karo
         templates/index.json mein section reference

STEP 8: Test karo
         Customizer mein dekho — settings kaam karti hain?

STEP 9: Mobile check karo
         Responsive hai?

STEP 10: Publish karo
          Theme publish — live ho gaya!
```

