Technical Implementation (simplified):

// predictive-search.js logic:
class PredictiveSearch {
  onInput(searchTerm) {
    // Debounce: wait 300ms after last keystroke
    clearTimeout(this.timeout);
    this.timeout = setTimeout(() => {
      this.fetchResults(searchTerm);
    }, 300);
  }
  
  async fetchResults(query) {
    const response = await fetch(
      `/search/suggest.json?q=${query}&resources[type]=product,collection,article&resources[limit]=4`
    );
    const data = await response.json();
    this.renderResults(data);
  }
}
IF-THEN Logic:

IF:   assets/predictive-search.js remove karo
THEN: Search bar type karte waqt KUCH nahi hoga
      Customer ko Enter press karna padega → full page search
      = Slow experience, less conversion

IF:   Debounce time bahut kam (e.g., 50ms)
THEN: Har keystroke pe API call = SERVER OVERLOAD
      Rate limit hit ho sakta hai
